videos.description: Trevon Bluiett gets the rebound and finds Kaiser Gates down court who makes the bucket for Xavier.
videos.headline: Bluiett connects with Gates for fast-break layup

videos.description: Justin Roberts gets past J.P. Macura and makes the jumper to tie the game against Xavier.
videos.headline: DePaul's Roberts beats Macura with quick jumper

videos.description: DePaul gets a turnover and Max Strus drains a 3-pointer on the other end to extend DePaul's early lead over Xavier.
videos.headline: DePaul stays hot with Strus 3-pointer

videos.description: Quentin Goodin drives in for the layup and draws contact as Xavier tries to come back against DePaul.
videos.headline: Goodin answers with and-1 bucket

videos.description: Kerem Kanter rebounds and finds Trevon Bluiett down court who finishes with the layup for Xavier.
videos.headline: Bluiett energizes crowd with fast layup

videos.description: Quentin Goodin intercepts a pass and throws it down on the other end for Xavier.
videos.headline: Goodin gets big steal and slam vs. DePaul

videos.description: Jordan Roberts blocks a shot and finds a way to gain control of the ball to give DePaul possession.
videos.headline: Roberts shuts down Xavier with big block

videos.description: J.P. Macura intercepts a pass and gets it to Quentin Goodin who elevates for the slam to extend Xavier's lead in the final seconds.
videos.headline: Xavier seals win with steal-and-slam
